articles.title: Suspect in assassination of Charlie Kirk arrested on suspicion of capital murder, weapons and obstruction offenses
articles.description: Tyler Robinson has been arrested in connection to the death of Charlie Kirk and is facing multiple charges [3, 4, 5].

articles.title: Government shutdown draws near as Democrats push for healthcare funding

articles.title: Bolsonaro sentenced to 27 years for plotting military coup in Brazil
articles.description: Former Brazilian President Jair Bolsonaro has been sentenced to 27 years in prison for plotting a military coup [1, 5].
